data.description: Horse property close to town!! This fully remodeled modular home has a beautiful addition added on making this charmer a 7 bedroom, 3 bathroom home located on 5 acres all fenced in with 2 outbuildings! Stainless steal appliances in the kitchen with a large pantry, a beautiful fireplace and the master bedroom has large walk-in closet!!So many great features to mention in this home to include main floor laundry and a jacuzzi tub! Please call  Jessica Little 406-799-1734 or your real estate professional
